96w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/remnant-2-trivium-matt-heafy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/remnant-2-trivium-matt-heafy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trivium">Trivium</a>的 Matt Heafy 创作并录制了一首新歌来支持《魂类》射击游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/remnant-2"><em>《Remnant 2》</em></a> ，名为“Wielder Of The Plague”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/features/gaming-features/triviums-matt-heafy-talks-loving-call-of-duty-and-final-fantasy-in-playback-3430960">Trivium 的马特·希菲 (Matt Heafy) 在“回放”中畅谈对《使命召唤》和《最终幻想》的喜爱</a></strong></li></ul><p>目前，只有《瘟疫持有者》的编辑版本可以与<em>《Remnant 2》</em>的新预告片一起聆听。完整的歌曲将在发行商 Gearbox Publishing 的官方 YouTube 频道上发布。看看下面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="遗迹2 |欧盟荣誉预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LpNdu5Bw62E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，在 Trivium 的欧洲巡演结束后，粉丝们将能够观看 Heafy 穿越<em>《遗迹 2》</em>世界的一系列直播。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/gunfire-games">Gunfire Games</a>的<em>《遗迹 2》</em>取得了巨大成功，发布后几天内在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a>上售出了 100 万份。此外，该游戏培养了一个好奇的社区， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/remnant-2-has-a-class-that-can-only-be-found-through-datamining-3476336">数据挖掘者为他们的努力发现了一个新的角色类别</a>。</p><p>这位歌手和吉他手是电子游戏的忠实粉丝，并将其作为灵感来源。 For example, the song &#39;The Calamity&#39; on Trivium&#39;s Shogun album has a reference to Jenova, the alien that is said to be Sephiroth&#39;s “mother” in <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-7"><em>Final Fantasy 7</em></a> .</p><p> “The first time I heard the music in <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/doom"><em>DOOM</em></a> (I was 11) – I knew someday I wanted to make music like this in video games. I didn&#39;t even know about metal or that the music in that game was metal,” said Heafy in a press release.</p><p> “Fast forward to 2023. I am so excited – honoured – privileged –and thankful to say I&#39;ve been asked to compose some music inspired by <em>Remnant 2</em> for the promotion of the game. I can&#39;t wait for you to hear this,” he concluded.</p><p> In other gaming news, Gunfire Games has acknowledged the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/remnant-2-is-getting-cross-play-and-new-archetypes-in-dlc-3479801">multitude of requests for cross play</a> and is “actively working” on giving the fans what they want.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/triviums-matt-heafy-reveals-a-new-song-for-remnant-2-3483882">Trivium&#39;s Matt Heafy reveals a new song for &#39;Remnant 2&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
